# Local private notes and reference checkouts.
# WARNING: `Notes/` matches `notes/` too on case-insensitive
# filesystems (default on macOS/Windows). Git does not allow
# `!notes/qa/`-style re-inclusion under an ignored parent
# directory, so we use a dedicated tracked path for QA artefacts.
# See `qa-artifacts/` for screenshots / repro captures.
Notes/
References/

# OS/editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
